import React, { Component } from 'react';
import TextField from '@material-ui/core/TextField';
import Dialog from '@material-ui/core/Dialog';
import DialogActions from '@material-ui/core/DialogActions';
import DialogContent from '@material-ui/core/DialogContent';
import DialogContentText from '@material-ui/core/DialogContentText';
import DialogTitle from '@material-ui/core/DialogTitle';
import { Button } from '@material-ui/core';

class AddPessoa extends Component { 
    
    state = {

    }

    render() {

        const styles = theme => ({
              marginRight: 2
          });    

        return(
            <Dialog
            open={this.props.open}
            >
                <DialogTitle>Adicionar</DialogTitle>
                <DialogContent>
                <DialogContentText>
                    Preencha os campos abaixo para adicionar uma nova pessoa
                </DialogContentText>
                <TextField
                    autoFocus
                    margin="dense"
                    id="nome"
                    label="Nome"
                    type="text"
                    fullWidth
                />
                <TextField
                    margin="dense"
                    id="cpf"
                    label="CPF"
                    type="text"
                    fullWidth
                />
                <TextField
                    margin="dense"
                    id="email"
                    label="email"
                    type="email"
                    fullWidth
                />
                <TextField
                    margin="dense"
                    id="telefone"
                    label="telefone"
                    type="text"
                    fullWidth
                />
                <TextField
                    margin="dense"
                    id="celular"
                    label="celular"
                    type="text"
                    fullWidth
                />  
                <TextField
                    margin="dense"
                    id="cep"
                    label="CEP"
                    type="text"
                />
                <TextField
                    margin="dense"
                    id="telefone"
                    label="telefone"
                    type="text"
                />
                <TextField
                    margin="dense"
                    id="uf"
                    label="cód. uf"
                    type="text"
                />
                <TextField
                    margin="dense"
                    id="cidade"
                    label="cód. cidade"
                    type="text"
                />
                <TextField
                    style = {styles.marginRight}
                    margin="dense"
                    id="municipio"
                    label="cód. município"
                    type="text"
                />
                <TextField
                    style = {styles.marginRight}
                    margin="dense"
                    id="sexo"
                    label="sexo"
                    type="text"
                />
                <TextField
                    style = {styles.marginRight}
                    InputLabelProps={{ shrink: true }}
                    margin="dense"
                    id="data_nascimento"
                    label="data de nascimento"
                    type="date"
                />                                                                                                    
    {/* "codigo_faixa_etaria": 1,
    "codigo_estado_civil": 1,
    "classe_social": "M",
    "codigo_instrucao": 1,
    "codigo_renda": 1,
    "codigo_profissao": 1,
    "codigo_posicao_trabalho": 1,
    "imovel": "praia",
    "funcionario": "empregada",
    "moradia": "Casa propria",
    "possui_carro": 1,
    "raca": "branca" */}
                </DialogContent>
                <DialogActions>
                <Button onClick={this.handleClose} color="primary">
                    Cancelar
                </Button>
                <Button onClick={this.handleClose} color="primary">
                    Adicionar
                </Button>
                </DialogActions>
          </Dialog>
        );
    }
}

export default AddPessoa;
